msgid ""
"Restores high-frequency clarity (sibilants like \"s\", \"sh\") after "
"suppression. Lower only if your voice already sounds harsh."
msgstr ""
"Taastab kõrgsagedusliku selguse (sibilandid nagu \"s\", \"š\") pärast "
"summutust. Alanda ainult siis, kui su hääl juba kõlab karmilt."

# File: biglinux-noise-reduction-
