# File: biglinux-noise-reduction-
# pipewire/src/biglinux_microphone/ui/main_view.py, line: 310
#: src/ui/views/output.rs:40
msgid "AI noise reduction"
msgstr "Tehisintellekti mürasummutus"

#: src/ui/views/output.rs:44
msgid "Audio enhancements"
msgstr "Helitöötlus"

#: src/ui/views/output.rs:59
msgid ""
"10-band parametric EQ on what you hear. Pick a preset or drag each band "
"between -40 dB and +40 dB."
msgstr ""
"10-ribaline parameetriline ekvalaiser selleks, mida sa kuuled. Vali "
"eelseadistus või lohista iga riba vahemikus -40 dB kuni +40 dB."

#: src/ui/views/output.rs:95 src/ui/views/simple.rs:179
msgid "System sound"
msgstr "Süsteemi heli"

#: src/ui/views/output.rs:96 src/ui/views/simple.rs:180
msgid ""
"Cleans background noise from everything you hear before it reaches your "
"speakers."
msgstr ""
"Puhastab taustamüra kõigest, mida kuulete, enne kui see teie kõlaritesse "
"jõuab."

#: src/ui/views/output.rs:131
msgid ""
"Restores high-frequency clarity after suppression. Lower only if the source "
"already sounds harsh."
msgstr ""
"Taastab kõrgsagedusliku selguse pärast summutust. Alanda ainult siis, kui "
"allikas juba kõlab karmilt."

#: src/ui/views/output.rs:162
msgid "Cuts low-frequency rumble from playback — wind, AC noise."
msgstr ""
"Lõikab madalsagedusliku vibreerimise taasesitusest — tuul, konditsioneeri "
"müra."

#: src/ui/views/output.rs:181
msgid ""
"Mutes playback during silent moments so you don't hear hiss between words."
msgstr ""
"Vaigistab taasesituse vaiksetel hetkedel, et sa ei kuuleks susinat sõnade "
"vahel."

#: src/ui/views/output.rs:211
msgid ""
"Evens out volume across loud and quiet speakers — useful for meetings with "
"mixed mic levels."
msgstr ""
"Ühtlustab helitugevust valjude ja vaiksete kõlarite vahel — kasulik "
"koosolekutel, kus mikrofoni tasemed on erinevad."

